file.name: simple-has-refs.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: unit test
  version: 0.0.1
components:
  schemas:
    CustomerType:
      type: string
      example: Example value
    Customer:
      properties:
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        heightMetres:
          type: number
        type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/CustomerType'
        friends:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Customer'
        favouritePartner:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Customer'
      required:
        - firstName
        - lastName
        - type
